Class Pair

  • java.lang.Object
    • app.Pair
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Pair>

    public class Pair
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Pair>
    A Pair consists of a shortForm Opus output and a longForm Opus output. Used by the GUI for displaying appropriate search output.
    Author:
    David Wickizer
